{"tid":970951,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[召喚串嘴撚] 你地喺Game入面試過／見過最串嘅人喺點？","createTime":"2019-01-06T09:30:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-08T01:58:11.000Z","uid":229553,"like":5,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"5ec265b3d71045e2225744ee2c40de866f5d5bec","tid":970951,"uid":229553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T09:30:45.000Z","msg":"見到篇文諗起以前自己點串人<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當年玩信長，好鬼小學雞，有人入場一定會打句「跪求一敗」, 45 no re, 35 no re<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n玩19 online game 係公頻互屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好幼稚但真喺好多回憶，你地又有無試過／見過最串嘅人喺點？<br />\n<br />\n-On the 8th day god saw that people are hungry so he made botlane.<br />\n在第八天，上帝看到了人們在挨餓，於是上帝創造了下路（feed，餵食，在遊戲中有送頭養肥之意）<br />\n-The scuttle crab applies more jungle pressure than you.<br />\n河蟹給野區的壓力都比你給的多<br />\n-I&rsquo;ll trade you 4 cannon creeps for our XXX_champ.<br />\n/all 我用我們這邊這個人換你們四輛砲車<br />\n-The only thing you carry is an extra chromosome.<br />\n你唯一carry了的東西（既指攜帶又指遊戲裡的carry）就是一條額外染色體<br />\n<br />\n【Reddit分享】英雄聯盟裡你見過最厲害的嘴炮是？<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.fighterstudiohk.com/news/%E3%80%90reddit%E5%88%86%E4%BA%AB%E3%80%91%E8%8B%B1%E9%9B%84%E8%81%AF%E7%9B%9F%E8%A3%A1%E4%BD%A0%E8%A6%8B%E9%81%8E%E6%9C%80%E5%8E%B2%E5%AE%B3%E7%9A%84%E5%98%B4%E7%82%AE%E6%98%AF%EF%BC%9F/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fighterstudiohk.com%2Fnews%2F%25E3%2580%2590reddit%25E5%2588%2586%25E4%25BA%25AB%25E3%2580%2591%25E8%258B%25B1%25E9%259B%2584%25E8%2581%25AF%25E7%259B%259F%25E8%25A3%25A1%25E4%25BD%25A0%25E8%25A6%258B%25E9%2581%258E%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%258E%25B2%25E5%25AE%25B3%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%2598%25B4%25E7%2582%25AE%25E6%2598%25AF%25EF%25BC%259F%2F&d=q1qTK65wSt509qYE28h0Jf7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=5be1a281\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.fighterstudiohk.com/news/%E3%80%90reddit%E